WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.541
Predictive Analysis: You are engaging a tier-one enterprise where the

00:00:04.541 --> 00:00:09.082
marketing team is eager to deploy AppsFlyer, but the procurement

00:00:09.082 --> 00:00:13.622
department is highly cost-sensitive and blocking the deal due to

00:00:13.622 --> 00:00:18.163
budget constraints. Privately formulate a written prediction on how introducing

00:00:18.163 --> 00:00:22.704
the AWS Marketplace alters the negotiation dynamics. The causal logic:

00:00:22.704 --> 00:00:27.245
By routing the transaction through the AWS Marketplace, the customer

00:00:27.245 --> 00:00:31.786
taps into broader corporate cloud commitments rather than limited departmental

00:00:31.786 --> 00:00:36.326
budgets. This fundamental reduction in buyer cost-sensitivity establishes an insurmountable

00:00:36.326 --> 00:00:40.867
competitive advantage over rivals like Adjust, Singular, and Kochava, completely

00:00:40.867 --> 00:00:45.408
dismantling complex stakeholder objections before they even arise.
